description: Offering a perfect blend of great coffee, delightful desserts, and familial & friendly service, Moonwood Coffee Co is fully equipped and eager to help the morning crowds of Orange County start their day off the right way.With its modern yet vintage aesthetic, this trailer gives off the sweetest disposition. You simply must try their delicious selection of hot & cold brewed coffee concoctions, including their famously tasty Affogato- rich and creamy vanilla gelato topped with a shot of hot espresso. For all this and more, make your way to this trailer soon, and also know that Moonwood Coffee Co makes for an impeccable beverage provider in case there’s a wedding, party, or big event that you’re planning.
name: Moonwood Coffee Co
